requirement_issues.requirement_text: The system shall operate on a system capable of multi-processing.

issues.description: The term 'multi-processing' is vague - does this refer to multi-core, multi-threaded, or distributed processing?
issues.suggested_fix: Specify the exact type of multi-processing required (e.g., 'The system shall support parallel processing across at least 4 CPU cores')

requirement_issues.requirement_text: The system shall operate on a system capable of near-real time execution of instructions.

issues.description: 'Near-real time' is subjective and not measurable
issues.suggested_fix: Quantify the acceptable latency (e.g., 'The system shall respond to inputs within 100ms 95% of the time')

requirement_issues.requirement_text: SH system shall be usable by those with slight eye loss.

issues.description: 'Slight eye loss' is not a standard accessibility term
issues.suggested_fix: Reference WCAG standards (e.g., 'The system shall comply with WCAG 2.1 Level AA for visual accessibility')

requirement_issues.requirement_text: System shall be easy to use.

issues.description: Subjective requirement that cannot be objectively verified
issues.suggested_fix: Define measurable usability metrics (e.g., '90% of users shall complete primary tasks without assistance within 5 minutes')

requirement_issues.requirement_text: SH shall have a reverse osmosis water purification system.

issues.description: Conflicts with REQ-022 which requires a non-filtered system
issues.suggested_fix: Clarify if both filtered and non-filtered systems should coexist or if this is an either/or requirement

requirement_issues.requirement_text: System shall not interfere in any way with detector's manufacturer's operating procedures.

issues.description: May be impossible to guarantee without knowing all possible detector manufacturers' procedures
issues.suggested_fix: Specify supported detector models or define an interface standard

requirement_issues.requirement_text: System may skip commercials when system is able to detect the commercial.

issues.description: Commercial detection is non-trivial and may have legal implications
issues.suggested_fix: Clarify detection method (e.g., using broadcast flags when available) and any legal restrictions

requirement_issues.requirement_text: System shall accept one-button touch support for incorporating DVD videos into digital library, where law and technology provide.

issues.description: 'Where law and technology provide' is too vague
issues.suggested_fix: Specify regions/legal jurisdictions and technical formats supported

domain_model_issues.description: System class has no attributes/methods despite being central to all functionality
domain_model_issues.suggested_fix: Add core attributes like systemStatus, version, etc. and methods like initialize(), shutdown()

domain_model_issues.description: Missing attributes for transaction rate and redundancy which are key requirements
domain_model_issues.suggested_fix: Add attributes like transactionCapacity, isRedundant, backupSchedule

domain_model_issues.description: Current 1-to-many relationship doesn't reflect redundancy requirement
domain_model_issues.suggested_fix: Change to 1-to-2..* to enforce at least two databases for failover

domain_model_issues.description: Missing pet/human differentiation capability mentioned in requirements
domain_model_issues.suggested_fix: Add method differentiateMotion(source) and attribute detectionSensitivity

domain_model_issues.description: Missing attributes to support playlist naming and description requirements
Missing portion control and monitoring capabilities
domain_model_issues.suggested_fix: Add attributes portionSize, foodLevel and methods dispenseFood(), checkLevels()

domain_model_issues.description: No class exists to handle the numerous notification requirements throughout the system
domain_model_issues.suggested_fix: Add NotificationSystem class with methods sendAlert(), logNotification() and relationships to all systems that generate alerts

domain_model_issues.description: Current 1:1 relationship doesn't reflect requirement for multiple pet bowls
domain_model_issues.suggested_fix: Change to 1:1..* to support multiple watering stations

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for system initialization and shutdown procedures
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall have defined initialization procedures that verify all connected subsystems are operational before entering normal operation mode. The system shall also have graceful shutdown procedures that ensure all data is saved and subsystems are properly deactivated.
missing_requirements.rationale: Any complex system needs proper initialization and shutdown procedures to ensure reliable operation and data integrity. The domain model shows many subsystems that need coordinated startup and shutdown.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for system-wide error handling and recovery
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall implement comprehensive error handling that logs all errors, attempts automatic recovery where possible, and provides appropriate notifications to users when manual intervention is required.
missing_requirements.rationale: With numerous interconnected subsystems, robust error handling is essential to maintain system stability and user confidence.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for user authentication and authorization
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall implement role-based access control with at least three distinct roles (admin, standard user, guest) with different permission levels for system configuration and operation.
missing_requirements.rationale: Given the security-sensitive nature of many functions (door locks, security cameras), proper authentication and authorization mechanisms are essential but currently unspecified.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for system-wide configuration management
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall provide a unified interface for backing up, restoring, and transferring all system configurations, including user preferences, device settings, and automation rules.
missing_requirements.rationale: With hundreds of configurable parameters across multiple subsystems, users need a way to manage configurations holistically.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for system health monitoring
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall continuously monitor the health status of all connected subsystems and components, providing real-time status displays and proactive notifications about potential issues.
missing_requirements.rationale: Given the complexity shown in the domain model, comprehensive health monitoring is needed to maintain system reliability.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for integration between security subsystems
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall coordinate between motion detectors, security cameras, and door lock systems to automatically record video when motion is detected near entry points and maintain a security event log.
missing_requirements.rationale: The domain model shows these security components but requirements don't specify how they should work together.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for HVAC system maintenance alerts
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall monitor HVAC system operation and notify users when maintenance activities are recommended based on usage patterns and manufacturer guidelines.
missing_requirements.rationale: HVAC systems require regular maintenance, but current requirements only cover basic operation, not maintenance needs.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for water purification system maintenance
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall track filter usage in the water purification system and notify users when filters need replacement based on both time elapsed and water volume processed.
missing_requirements.rationale: Water filtration systems require regular filter changes, but current requirements only mention cleaning notifications.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for alternative energy system integration with main power
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall manage the integration of alternative energy sources with the main power grid, including automatic switching between power sources based on availability and cost optimization.
missing_requirements.rationale: The domain model includes alternative energy but requirements don't specify how it integrates with the home's power system.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for pet feeding system emergency operation
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall have a manual override mechanism for the pet feeding system that allows food to be dispensed even when normal power or system operation is disrupted.
missing_requirements.rationale: Pet care systems need fail-safe mechanisms to ensure pets are cared for during system outages.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for video library content organization
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall automatically organize video content in the library based on metadata and user preferences, including creation of collections, recommendations, and smart playlists.
missing_requirements.rationale: With extensive video recording capabilities, users need intelligent organization features to manage their content.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for audio system multi-room synchronization
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall support synchronized audio playback across multiple rooms with adjustable delay compensation to account for different room sizes and locations.
missing_requirements.rationale: Whole-home audio systems need synchronization features for seamless listening experiences.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for appliance controller safety interlocks
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall implement safety interlocks that prevent potentially dangerous combinations of appliance operations (e.g., space heaters and drapes, or stove and ventilation).
missing_requirements.rationale: Automated appliance control needs safety mechanisms to prevent hazardous conditions.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for water recovery system overflow handling
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall monitor water recovery system capacity and implement overflow prevention measures when storage approaches maximum capacity during heavy rainfall.
missing_requirements.rationale: Water recovery systems need overflow management to prevent property damage.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for radon detector calibration
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall track radon detector calibration status and notify users when calibration is required according to manufacturer specifications.
missing_requirements.rationale: Radon detectors require periodic calibration to maintain accuracy, but this isn't mentioned in requirements.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for system-wide software update mechanism
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall provide a secure mechanism for updating all system software components, including verification of update integrity and rollback capability if updates fail.
missing_requirements.rationale: Complex systems require a reliable update mechanism to maintain security and functionality over time.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for pet litter box waste capacity monitoring
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall monitor waste capacity in pet litter boxes and notify users when waste containers need emptying, in addition to odor-based cleaning notifications.
missing_requirements.rationale: Current requirements only mention odor-based cleaning, but waste capacity is also an important factor.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for window controller weather protection
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall automatically close windows when rain is detected or when severe weather alerts are received from weather services.
missing_requirements.rationale: Automated windows need weather protection features to prevent water damage.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for security camera data retention policy
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall implement configurable retention policies for security camera footage, with different retention periods for normal operation versus security-triggered recordings.
missing_requirements.rationale: Security systems need clear data retention policies to balance storage needs with security requirements.

missing_requirements.description: Missing requirement for system-wide energy usage monitoring
missing_requirements.suggested_requirement: The system shall monitor and report energy usage across all connected systems and appliances, providing breakdowns by subsystem and recommendations for energy savings.
missing_requirements.rationale: With numerous energy-using subsystems, comprehensive energy monitoring would be valuable but isn't specified.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system shall operate on a system capable of multi-processing.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system shall operate on a system capable of multi-processing to ensure efficient handling of concurrent tasks. [Rationale: Improves system performance. Priority: High. Acceptance Criteria: System successfully executes multiple processes simultaneously.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and acceptance criteria clarifies the purpose and how to verify the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system shall operate on a system capable of near-real time execution of instructions.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system shall operate on a system capable of near-real time execution of instructions to ensure timely responses. [Rationale: Ensures responsiveness. Priority: High. Acceptance Criteria: System responds to stimuli within 500ms.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and acceptance criteria clarifies the purpose and how to verify the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system shall service triggers or stimuli in no more than 500 milliseconds.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system shall service triggers or stimuli in no more than 500 milliseconds to ensure real-time responsiveness. [Rationale: Critical for user experience. Priority: High. Acceptance Criteria: Measured response time ≤500ms.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and priority clarifies the importance of the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system shall have a database associated with it that can handle transaction processing at a rate of 1000 transactions per minute.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system shall have a database associated with it that can handle transaction processing at a rate of 1000 transactions per minute to ensure high throughput. [Rationale: Supports system scalability. Priority: High. Acceptance Criteria: Database processes ≥1000 transactions/minute under load.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and acceptance criteria clarifies the purpose and how to verify the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system shall have redundant databases for fail over purposes.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system shall have redundant databases for fail over purposes to ensure high availability. [Rationale: Minimizes downtime. Priority: High. Acceptance Criteria: System switches to backup database within 1 second of primary failure.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and acceptance criteria clarifies the purpose and how to verify the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system shall perform periodical offsite and onsite backups of all configuration and reporting data.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system shall perform periodical offsite and onsite backups of all configuration and reporting data to ensure data recovery. [Rationale: Prevents data loss. Priority: Medium. Acceptance Criteria: Backups occur daily and are verified for integrity.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and acceptance criteria clarifies the purpose and how to verify the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system shall support wired Ethernet for 1 gigabit per second, and contain cat 6e cabling.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system shall support wired Ethernet for 1 gigabit per second, and contain cat 6e cabling to ensure high-speed data transfer. [Rationale: Supports bandwidth-intensive applications. Priority: Medium. Acceptance Criteria: Network throughput ≥1 Gbps.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and acceptance criteria clarifies the purpose and how to verify the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system may contain separate SAN device for storage flexibility.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system may contain separate SAN device for storage flexibility to enhance scalability. [Rationale: Optional for future expansion. Priority: Low. Acceptance Criteria: SAN integrates seamlessly if present.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and priority clarifies the optional nature of the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: The system may contain separate video recorder/processor for process distribution.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: The system may contain separate video recorder/processor for process distribution to improve performance. [Rationale: Optional for load balancing. Priority: Low. Acceptance Criteria: Video processing is distributed if present.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and priority clarifies the optional nature of the requirement.

requirement_completeness.requirement_text: If system supports recording more than three television shows simultaneously, then system shall have separate video recorder.
requirement_completeness.suggested_improvement: If system supports recording more than three television shows simultaneously, then system shall have separate video recorder to ensure performance. [Rationale: Prevents resource contention. Priority: High. Acceptance Criteria: System records ≥4 shows without degradation.]
requirement_completeness.rationale: Adding rationale and acceptance criteria clarifies the purpose and how to verify the requirement.
